    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2). This specimen features the naturally aspirated 3.8L flat-six engine equipped with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), producing 385 hp with a razor-sharp throttle response. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle and a factory-ordered limited-slip differential. The chassis is bolstered by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing exceptional damping control and roll stiffness. Every mechanical component, from the dry-sump lubrication system to the four-piston monobloc calipers, is in flawless operating condition. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the undercarriage remains free of any oxidation or fluid seepage. A mechanically transparent example for the purist collector.",
